"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:CompileBasic\" visibility=\"visible\">Compiles the Basic macro.</ahelp> You need to compile a macro after you make changes to it, or if the macro uses single or procedure steps."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:CompileBasic\" visibility=\"visible\">ຄອມໄພລ໌ມາກໂຄຣ Basic.</ahelp> ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຄອມໄພລ໌ມາກໂຄຣຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ມີການປ່ຽນແປງ, ຫຼື ຖ້າມາກໂຄຣນັ້ນໃຊ້ຂັ້ນຕອນດຽວ ຫຼື ຂັ້ນຕອນຂະບວນການ."

